item.title: CVE-2017-16200|2024-09-17T02:11:08.457Z -- hackerone -- uv-tj-demo%20node%20module
item.description: uv-tj-demo is a static file server. uv-tj-demo is vulnerable to a directory traversal issue, giving an attacker access to the filesystem by placing "../" in the url.
